### List inquiries
GET http://localhost:3000/inquiries

### Get allowed transitions
GET http://localhost:3000/inquiries/inquiry_id_here/allowed-transitions

### Transition inquiry status
POST http://localhost:3000/inquiries/inquiry_id_here/transitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toStatus": "need_clarification",
  "reason": "Customer did not provide full technical parameters.",
  "operatorType": "human"
}
